BugInstance.message: Method org.apache.shardingsphere.data.pipeline.cdc.client.CDCClient.startInternal(String, int) needlessly boxes a boolean constant
Unconstrained method org.apache.shardingsphere.data.pipeline.cdc.client.handler.CDCRequestHandler.processDataRecords(ChannelHandlerContext, DataRecordResult) converts checked exception to unchecked

Method org.apache.shardingsphere.data.pipeline.cdc.client.handler.LoginRequestHandler.setLoginRequest(ChannelHandlerContext, CDCResponse, ClientConnectionContext) encodes String bytes without specifying the character encoding

org.apache.shardingsphere.data.pipeline.cdc.client.util.ProtobufAnyValueConverter.converProtobufTimestamp(Timestamp): 1st parameter 'timestamp' could be declared as com.google.protobuf.TimestampOrBuilder instead
Method org.apache.shardingsphere.data.pipeline.cdc.client.util.ProtobufAnyValueConverter.convertToObject(Any) returns different types of unrelated Objects
